CatDescriptText: Cutline of related image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, September 14, 1953, pg. A11 reads: "Married 52 Years - Mr. and Mrs. Thomas L. West celebrated 52 years of marriage last Friday with a family dinner at their home on Duff St. Mr. West is a successful mortician who recently celebrated 25 years in business. - "Teenie" Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Group portrait of Mr. and Mrs. Thomas L. West, celebrating their fifty-second wedding anniversary, standing behind desk surrounded by flowers, in West's Funeral Home, another version
